	<h1 class="title">热播剧《硅谷》中的“魔笛手”算法成真了？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/103970/small/103970.jpg?1431972719" alt="">
